Identity persists across multiple layers.  
Deep stability.

### 4.3 Distributed Continuity
Identity persists across diverse contexts.  
Flexible stability.

### 4.4 Recursive Continuity
Identity persists through self‑reference.  
Meta‑stability.

Geometry determines continuity strength.

