### 5.1 Stabilization
Continuity increases through:
- attractor reinforcement  
- narrative integration  
- boundary maintenance  

### 5.2 Destabilization
Continuity decreases through:
- contradiction amplification  
- attractor drift  
- boundary rupture  

### 5.3 Reorganization
Continuity shifts through:
- identity revision  
- narrative reconstruction  
- recursive reorientation  

Identity continuity evolves dynamically.

